===Adjective===
'''biblical'''
# of, or relating to, the [[Bible]]

# in accordance with the [[teaching]]s of the Bible (according to some interpretation of the later), e.g. "The [[biblical]] [[teaching]] is that...", "biblical morality", etc.

# of such an [[extreme]] that it far exceeds any previous record

